      "content": "thanks. i really don't want to go to the er if i don't have to, it's so expensive and i'm pretty sure i can just sleep through this. if i take the codeine and the ibuprofen, will that keep the pain down enough that it won't wake me up? also, should i eat a little something light like toast first so my stomach isn't empty when i take them?",
